Installation Notes:

SOURCE CODE install path
------------------------
Starting xIrc-2.3.8, a port to Qt-2.1.1 or higher is required. Working with the source, do

  tar zxf xIrc-2.3.8.tar.gz (for those using GNU tar) or

  gunzip -c xIrc-2.3.8.tar.gz | tar xf - (for those using non GNU tar).

cd xIrc-2.3.8

Set QTDIR=/path_to_qt211_base/ (e.g., QTDIR=/usr/lib/qt-2.1.1 for bash users)

Type
      ./configure
or
      ./configure --with-qt-libraries=$QTDIR/lib --with-qt-includes=$QTDIR/include

Type make (preferably GNU make).

After the compiling phase, type make install as root.

NOTE:
There is nolonger support for Qt-1.44.

REDHAT PACKAGE
--------------

rpm -ihv xIrc-2.3.7-1.i386.rpm

SOLARIS 7 x86 PACKAGE
---------------------

Discontinued.
